title: SkyFall Black hosting try outs for gold-plat team jungle and mid laners
body: we are looking for like minded individuals who want to be part of a new team. what I mean by that is we are starting from the ground up, means must have dedication in and out side of practice, patients from forming a team, finding the right group to mesh well, and willing to thrive through loses, wins and any thing else. we are looking for jungle and mid try outs currently, link your op.gg and a small paragraph about your self. again we need people willing to have the right mind set for the team.

replies.body:
Hey guys! I've been playing since season 2, and I'm in the navy. I'm also very dedicated to playing the game, and playing with a team, and becoming the best. I understand that becoming the best would take a considerable amount of time, but I believe if the team I join is dedicated enough, then it'll all be worth it through the grind. 
 http://na.op.gg/summoner/userName=bimbim
BimBim

What's up guys, I have been playing league since season 4 and have made it the highest to my promos for Platinum and currently G1 in Flex so many team games, and G4 in Solo/Duo.   I main mid lane and support, with champions in the mid lane like Galio, Ryze, Orianna, LB, and Syndra.  Here is my link to my op.gg. http://na.op.gg/summoner/userName=Insuuuhnity
